---
title: Kale, Brussels & Orange Salad with Feta plus Couscous, Red Wine Vinaigrette & Garlicky Panko
description: As far as hearty salads go, this one reigns supreme! You’ll sautée shredded Brussels sprouts with shallot and garlic, then toss with kale, nutty pearl couscous, and juicy fresh orange in a tangy homemade red wine vinaigrette. A sprinkle each of briny crumbled feta and garlicky breadcrumbs top off these bright, nourishing bowls.
